#. Tag: para
#: ch09.xml:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While any license that is free is also open source, and vice versa (with a "
"few minor exceptions), people tend to pick one term and stick with it. In "
"general, those who prefer \"free software\" are more likely to have a "
